#libIMAC-opengl HOWTO-test

***
Simple test
***

0. Ensure you have the whole libIMAC directory, otherwise you won't have CxxTest.
1. compile and install libIMAC-opengl (see HOWTO-build)
2. cd libIMAC-opengl/tests/
3. make
4. enjoy \o/
